| `--deep-50` | *(computed)* | Near-white, hero section text on dark bg |
| `--deep-100` | *(computed)* | Off-white surfaces in light mode |
| `--deep-200` | *(computed)* | Subtle dark-tinted borders |
| `--deep-300` | *(computed)* | Secondary text in dark contexts |
| `--deep-400` | *(computed)* | Tertiary text |
| `--deep-500` | *(computed)* | Mid-range, rarely used directly |
| `--deep-600` | *(computed)* | Strong dark fills |
| `--deep-700` | *(computed)* | Sidebar, nav backgrounds |
| `--deep-800` | *(computed)* | Card surfaces in dark mode |
