| `--gray-400` | Placeholder text, disabled text |
| `--gray-500` | Tertiary text |
| `--gray-600` | Secondary text |
| `--gray-700` | Primary text (light mode) |
| `--gray-800` | Strong headings |
| `--gray-900` | Maximum contrast text |
| `--gray-950` | Near-black |

